    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been totally babied, kept in a garage, and it still has that fresh feel every time you get behind the wheel. If you're looking for a total gem that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, you\u2019ve found it! Drop me a message if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 47250.0,
