    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a benchmark of atmospheric engineering. The S54 power plant has undergone a comprehensive technical refresh, including a bespoke VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure long-term reciprocating integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission facilitates seamless gear synchronization, feeding a reinforced rear subframe and a variable M differential lock. Handling is razor-sharp, featuring a refreshed suspension geometry with polyurethane bushings for heightened lateral stiffness. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous response, while the engine maintains perfect compression across all six cylinders. This is a turn-key, concours-standard specimen for the enthusiast who demands mechanical transparency and peak performance.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
