      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This masterpiece remains in showroom condition, having been meticulously garage-kept and pampered by a single owner since its debut. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like luster without a single swirl mark or stone chip, while the interior retains that fresh, factory-clean scent, featuring pristine leather upholstery and untouched cabin trim. Mechanically, it is flawless; every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of records included. From the whisper-quiet idle to the seamless gear transitions, this car performs exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who refuses to compromise on quality, this is an investment-grade example that must be seen to be believed.",
